			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I think it's silly to come on these boards and dismiss spells as useless...I didn't use WoP for ages after people said it didn't do anything but it IS useful, just as I susupect word of shadow will be when I finally get to level 19:<BR>
<BR>
A) When in a group fighting 2 mobs this spell becomes more mana efficient than smite.<BR>
<BR>
B) When fighting 3 4 or even 5 mobs the AE spells become ridiculously mana efficient.<BR>
<BR>
C) You don't have to fumble around in a crowded melee trying to find the target you want to smite..just hit the spell button and keep healing your tanks.<BR>
<BR>
D) If you are fighting a couple of tiny mobs as well as the big ones this can be used to either kill them or take them off your tanks, who will probably be taking more notice of the bigger creatures.<BR>
<BR>
My advice to newbies is ignore all these posts and try the spell out for yourself. Just because someone else finds no use for it doesn't mean you wont. After all don't we want to be better clerics than the ones before us? :)<BR>
<BR>
-Levo<BR>
Lvl 17 Cleric Rodcet Nife Server
