				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				You must keep something in mind when casting AE spells, especially point blank ones like the word series. <BR>
<BR>
If the mobs dont have a built up hate list on someone else already they WILL all train on you.<BR>
<BR>
So yes it is very mana efficient for 3 plus targets, but say you and a tank are fighting 4 blues, or high greens. 3 Just went aggro on you and you are NOT going to cast anymore for the rest of that battle (assuming your tank isnt at 20% health or less, which in that case your dead also). Complaining to your tank that &quot;Ack! they are all on me, taunt them, attack them, I can't cast!&quot; is going to make you look VERY silly indeed for casting the Word.<BR>
<BR>
Word up!
